Task
Change the sign of the sum of numbers
Write a function called oppositeSum that takes three numbers a, b, c as arguments and returns the sum of these numbers with the opposite sign.
Example:
â€¢ function oppositeSum (1, 2, 3) must return -6;
â€¢ function oppositeSum (-1, -2, -3) must return 6;
â€¢ the oppositeSum (0, 1, -1) function must return 0.

Solution
function oppositeSum(a, b, c){
 let sum = a + b + c;
   if(sum > 0 || sum < 0) return (-sum);
     else if ( sum === 0) return 0;
}
